description:

Wenona is known for her headlocks. But her style of headlocks have been banned in US rules and she hasn't adapted to the new "arm in Headlock" style that is allowed so now she needs to find something else to rely on.....enter.... the power of her legs. Wenona uses her long, strong legs to control her opponent. These two leggy girls make a great match up. They both get hot and sweaty which looks beautiful as they torture each other on the mat. Winner Tramples the loser with her Bare feet.
